version_description:
We constantly update our app to offer you an ever better service. With this latest update, we have improved the user experience and performance.
<br>How does it work?
<br>- Sign in;
<br>- Bring your device closer to the vending machine;
<br>- Top up your wallet with coins or credit card;
<br>- Enjoy your break!
<br>
<br>How can I access the service after the update?
<br>If you registered using your phone number but you no longer remember your PIN, check the message section of your device or request a new one by clicking on "New Pin".
